caught up in the Megs-Motor action) =P

Switchblade perks up as he hears about technical skills, "Hey 
Megs, I'd prolly be able to find out what makes you tick, or in your 
case something that is preventing you from ticking properly." He 
chuckles, "But first, i've got to go and get our last prisoner," He 
laughs to himself, and flies to get Symphony.
